prodNameC: 常盈黃體脂酮檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Progesterone Standards: 
One vial, labeled A, containing 0 ng/mL and five vials, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of
approximately 0.3, 1.0, 5.0, 20.0, and 60.0 ng/mL (1.0-190.8 nmol/L) of progesterone in serum with sodium
azide as a preservative. 
* DSL-3900 (500 Tubes) contains three sets of Standards.
Progesterone [I-125] Reagent: 
One bottle (DSL-3900), 55 mL each, containing <5 μCi (185 kBq) of [I-125]-labeled progesterone in a
protein-based buffer with sodium benzoate as a preservative. 
* DSL-3900 (500 Tubes) contains five vials of reagent.
Anti-Progesterone-Coated Tubes:

One hundred (100) or five hundred (500) plastic tubes with rabbit anti-progesterone immunoglobulin
immobilized to the inside wall of each tube. 
Progesterone Controls: 
Two vials, Levels I and II, containing low and high concentrations of progesterone in serum with sodium azide as a preservative. 
DSL-3900 (500 Tubes) contains three sets of Controls.

efficacy: 利用放射性免疫定量方法檢測血清或血漿中的黃體脂酮蒙荷爾蒙。
